      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but that's exactly my worry. if i take it, i'm scared i'll wake up at 3am with a massive crash because there's basically no glucose in my system from that salad. if my current reading is stable, isn't the main goal just to prevent a low? wouldn't skipping it just be the most common sense way to bridge the gap until i can call my doctor on monday?",
